Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.53,0:03:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.70,0:03:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.61,0:03:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh... cantik sekali...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.99,0:03:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... baunya enak sekali...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.29,0:03:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Komi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.45,0:03:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rupanya, orang ini, \N  di hari pertama sekolahnya,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.21,0:03:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}telah memposisikan dirinya  \N  sebagai madonna sekolah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.09,0:03:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yah,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.42,0:03:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aku bukannya tidak senang duduk di  \N sebelah siswi tercantik di sekolah,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.01,0:03:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tapi entah kenapa...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.47,0:03:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aku merasa dikepung oleh para pembunuh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.47,0:03:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Kubur dia hidup-hidup!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.72,0:03:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Kuburkan dia, kubur dia!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.80,0:03:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Kuburkan dia, kubur dia!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.80,0:03:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Begitu dia mati,  \N aku akan duduk di sampingnya..!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.22,0:03:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Tadano... kan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.39,0:03:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kehidupan SMA Tadano-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.19,0:03:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}telah sudah bergejolak sejak hari pertama.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.17,0:03:53.67,no border,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\pos(196.8,66.8)\1a&H77}Komi-san
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.61,0:03:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Pengenalan diri.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.03,0:04:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Uhuhuhuhh... Aku..Agari!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.28,0:04:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhuhuhhh... sasasasa... \N  lamlmalamlam...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.74,0:04:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ssssalamm kennnaall...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.74,0:04:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Aha!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.29,0:04:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Agari-san terlalu bersemangat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.91,0:04:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Agari-san terlalu bersemangat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.70,0:04:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Wah... kelas ini sepertinya hangat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.00,0:04:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Lanjut.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.90,0:04:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.52,0:04:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.07,0:04:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.40,0:04:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahahhhh...
