Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.39,0:05:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ck.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.39,0:05:53.33,no border,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.2\c&H464345&\move(242.24,37.787,248.64,37.36,2,2921)}Ninja
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.48,0:05:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eeh... orang apa ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.35,0:05:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ah...  kalau tidak cepat, bisa bahaya–
